div.div:
Refactor SyncFilesNotificationService to use FlatBuffers instead of Protocol Buffers
- Removed Protocol Buffers dependency and related code from Lusp_SyncFilesNotificationService. - Deleted upload_file_info.proto file as it is no longer needed. - Implemented FlatBuffers serialization in Lusp_SyncFilesNotificationService. - Updated socketSendFunc to serialize and send data using FlatBuffers. - Adjusted logging to maintain consistency with new serialization method. - Minor formatting and cleanup in main.cpp for console output settings.
Refactor code structure and remove redundant changes

Refactor file handling to support UTF-16 encoding
- Updated CMakeUserPresets.json to change QML_DEBUG_ARGS and checksum. - Added new image files to the downloads directory. - Modified FileInfo.h to change string types to std::u16string for better Unicode support. - Updated FileInfoQtAdapter to accept std::u16string for file paths. - Changed SyncUploadQueue methods to accept std::u16string for file paths. - Enhanced logging to handle UTF-16 strings in log_headers.h and related files. - Refactored FileInfo.cpp to implement UTF-16 handling for file paths and names. - Updated FileListWidget and MainWindow to work with std::u16string. - Adjusted NotificationService to log file names in UTF-16. - Modified SyncUploadQueue and its private implementation to handle UTF-16 strings. - Added documentation for iconv conversions related to character encoding.
Refactor code structure and remove redundant changes
